--- SOURCE 45: 铜钴大涨、洛阳钼业却收21.98元：股价不涨反跌，到底为啥？ ---
URL: http://m.toutiao.com/group/7609691161196593710/?upstream_biz=VolcEngine

SUMMARY:
<summary>
The article explains why the stock price of Luoyang Molybdenum, a global copper and cobalt leader, fell despite significant increases in copper and cobalt prices. Copper prices rose 42% and cobalt prices surged 173%, yet the stock closed at 21.98 yuan, down over 5%. The decline is attributed to four main short-term factors: 1) Cobalt export quotas in the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC) limit short-term shipments, creating uncertainty as the company's 2026 cobalt production guidance of 11–12 tons exceeds its allocated quota of about 3.47 tons; 2) Profit-taking after the stock's prior 210% surge from 2025 lows; 3) A broader sell-off in the metals sector and weak market sentiment; and 4) The cobalt quota issue overshadowing copper's positive price impact. The author argues that the long-term investment thesis remains intact due to solid fundamentals, strong demand from新能源 (new energy) and储能 (energy storage), and the company's global diversification efforts. The advice is to monitor short-term quota adjustments and long-term supply-demand dynamics.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
商品价格猛涨，公司股价为啥不跟涨，反而往下走？, 铜价累计涨幅达到42%，钴价涨幅更是高达173%。, 刚果（金）出台了2026—2027年钴出口配额政策，全年总量9.66万吨，洛阳钼业拿到约35.9%，也就是3.47万吨左右。但公司给出的2026年钴产量指引是11—12万吨。, 股市里有句话：利好出尽是利空，利空出尽是利好。, 铜钴大涨是长期底气，股价回调是短期压力。
</key_excerpts>



